![Image alt]({{ site.baseurl }}/assets/img/people/Parperis_mugshot.jpg "Christopher Parperis")
Christopher joined the Wallace group in 2017, in collaboration with Oxford Nanopore Technologies. His PhD research utilises microscopy techniques, such as optical single channel recording and single molecule fluorescence tracking, to image the mechanism of DNA sensing in a protein nanopore.
